des: Zoo jumanji is an interactive game where you will face many animals with their amazing sounds. You have to recognise the animals in order to rescue them. it will enhance your knowledge and test your recognising skill. So, start exploring the zoo and keep enjoying.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
